rComments: Had him for toxicology in 3rd year; so funny and excludes a lot of material from lecture on midterm tests (i.e. you don't have to study so much!) Very informative.
LEGEND. Great prof,  he gets right down to the point and specifically tells you which slides to memorize and what we should know for the tests and exams. Cracks hilarious jokes sometimes as well.
Horrible Professor. This was my worst grade ever. Even though he gives out many bonus points, his tests are a hit or miss (mostly miss). Midterm average ranges around 40%
